Package: bcflib
Type: Package
Title: Utilities Function to manipulate bcf/vcf files in R
Version: 0.7.7-2
Date: 2025-04-29
Author: Sounkou Mahamane Toure
Maintainer: Sounkou Mahamane Toure <sounkoutoure@gmail.com>
Description: This package collated some quality of life utilites for BCF/VCF file manipulations in R. 
        It is based on the vcfppR package, which provides C++ library and R methods for parsing and manipulating VCF/BCF files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: GNU make, pkg-config
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.12), vcfppR (>= 0.7.7), vcfppR(<= 0.7.7)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, vcfppR
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
OS_type: unix
Remotes: Zilong-Li/vcfppR
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Encoding: UTF-8
